  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education of poor disabled Children in Peru</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project consists of facilitating the inclusion of poor children with disabilities in the regular education system in Ayacucho, Peru. This will be done through a personalized follow-up to the beneficiary children, giving them sessions of academic reinforcement, continuous visits of the schools, sensitization of teachers and classmates.  All this will be reinforced by the work of the multidisciplinary team of the Wasi Esperanza rehabilitation centre, that works more than 6 years in this area.</narrative>
  </description>
